prompts.frontCover:
**CROP-A-PALOOZA!** Here are 12 different crops from your original image. Use these as hints to get a better sense of the subjects and details.

**Front Cover Prompt:**

Epic comic book cover art for a birthday card, dynamic and action-packed scene. Illustrated versions of Jordan and Lao Lao from the reference photo are snowboarding down a steep, snowy mountain made entirely of giant sushi rolls. Jordan, in his maroon t-shirt and grey jacket from the photo, is in the foreground, expertly carving through the snow on his snowboard, kicking up a spray of white powder. He has a determined and joyful "game face" expression. Lao Lao, wearing her light-colored jacket and glasses from the photo, is slightly behind him on her own snowboard, laughing gleefully as she tries to catch up. The mountain is a surreal landscape of oversized California rolls, salmon nigiri, and shrimp tempura rolls, with nori-wrapped peaks and wasabi-green trees. In the background, a bright, explosive comic book "POW!" bubble adds to the action. Centered in a clear area of the bright blue sky, the text "Happy Birthday, Jordan!" is written in a bold, beautiful, and readable handwritten cursive script, colored in a vibrant yellow with a black outline to make it pop. The overall aesthetic is flat 2D art with bold outlines, vibrant Ben-Day dot shading, and a high-energy, humorous feel perfect for a comic book cover.
